OL,3,CSon of farmer who took own life says
OL,4,Ctax climbdown is 'best Christmas
OL,5,Cpresent'
OL,7,FA Barnsley farmer whose father killed
OL,8,Fhimself the day before last October's
OL,9,Fbudget after weeks of worrying about
OL,10,Finheritance tax changes has said the
OL,11,FGovernment's climbdown will be "the
OL,12,Fbest Christmas present for a lot of
OL,13,Ffarmers".
OL,15,FJohn Charlesworth, 78, who went by his
OL,16,Fmiddle name Philip, was found dead by
OL,17,Fhis son in a barn on their farm in
OL,18,FSilkstone on 29 October last year.
