OL,5,Cpresent'
OL,7,FAn inquest at Sheffield Coroner's
OL,8,FCourt heard that in the months before
OL,9,FRachel Reeves's budget, he had been
OL,10,F"growing more and more anxious about
OL,11,Finheritance tax and the implications
OL,12,Ffor the farm".
OL,14,FHis son Jonathan Charlesworth told the
OL,15,Finquest he believed his father wanted
OL,16,Fto "beat" the Government's proposals
OL,17,Fand "save the farm for future
OL,18,Fgenerations".
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@MO]xD@DOUxD@IO]yD@EOUzD@LO]
