OL,3,CSon of farmer who took own life says
OL,4,Ctax climbdown is 'best Christmas
OL,5,Cpresent'
OL,7,FReacting to Tuesday's news that the
OL,8,FGovernment will raise the inheritance
OL,9,Ftax relief threshold for farmers from
OL,10,F#1 million to #2.5 million, Jonathan
OL,11,FCharlesworth said that "pressure from
OL,12,Fthe industry has paid off".
OL,14,FHe said: "It is a step in the right
OL,15,Fdirection ` more farms will sleep
OL,16,Fbetter this Christmas without the
OL,17,Fthreat of inheritance tax looming over
OL,18,Fthem.
OL,26,@sD@XOUtD@ZO]vD@JOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
