OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F363A1766700283
OL,3,CSon of farmer who took own life says
OL,4,Ctax climbdown is 'best Christmas
OL,5,Cpresent'
OL,7,F"There will, however, be plenty of
OL,8,Flarger family farms that will have to
OL,9,Fplan for potential inheritance tax
OL,10,Fcosts and a further window for them to
OL,11,Fdo this would be beneficial.
OL,13,F"It's a welcome U-turn that won't
OL,14,Fbring back the lives lost over the
OL,15,Flast year or so due to the anxiety
OL,16,Fcaused, but will hopefully prevent a
OL,17,Fflood of suicides running up to the
OL,18,Fcommencement in April.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
