OL,7,F"Pressure from the industry has paid
OL,8,Foff ` this will be the best Christmas
OL,9,Fpresent for a lot of farmers."
OL,11,FJonathan Charlesworth said the change
OL,12,F"should have been researched and put
OL,13,Fout to review before any announcement
OL,14,Fwas made".
OL,16,F"But today we can celebrate a well-
OL,17,Ffought-for victory for our precious
OL,18,Fcountryside and the custodians of it,"
OL,19,Fhe added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@^O]tD@AOUvD@IO]xD@AOUzD@fO]
