OL,7,FThe change to the reforms initially
OL,8,Funveiled at Labour's first Budget last
OL,9,Fyear comes after ministers "listened
OL,10,Fto concerns" of the farming community
OL,11,Fand businesses, the Department for
OL,12,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,13,F(Defra) said on Tuesday 23 December.
OL,15,FThe original Treasury plans to raise
OL,16,Fmoney as farmers pass their businesses
OL,17,Ffrom generation to generation
OL,18,Ftriggered protests with tractors
OL,19,Foutside Parliament and criticism from
OL,20,Fsome Labour MPs in rural seats.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@LO]
