OL,3,CSon of farmer who took own life says
OL,4,Ctax climbdown is 'best Christmas
OL,5,Cpresent'
OL,7,FThe higher threshold, which will take
OL,8,Feffect in April, will allow spouses or
OL,9,Fcivil partners to pass on up to #5
OL,10,Fmillion in qualifying agricultural or
OL,11,Fbusiness assets between them before
OL,12,Fpaying inheritance tax ` on top of
OL,13,Fexisting allowances, Defra said.
OL,15,FAbove that allowance, farmers will get
OL,16,F50% relief on qualifying assets and
OL,17,Fwill pay a reduced effective rate of
OL,18,Fup to 20%, rather than the standard
OL,19,F40%.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
