OL,4,Ctax climbdown is 'best Christmas
OL,5,Cpresent'
OL,7,FThe number of estates facing higher
OL,8,Finheritance tax will be reduced from
OL,9,Faround 2,000 under the original plans
OL,10,Fto up to 1,100, hitting only the
OL,11,Flargest farms, according to the
OL,12,FGovernment.
OL,14,FFarmers currently do not pay
OL,15,Finheritance tax on agricultural and
OL,16,Fbusiness assets which they pass on.
OL,18,FUnder Labour's initial proposal, the
OL,19,Ffull 100% relief was to be restricted
OL,20,Fto the first #1 million of property.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
