OL,3,CSon of farmer who took own life says
OL,4,Ctax climbdown is 'best Christmas
OL,5,Cpresent'
OL,7,FJonathan Charlesworth told the
OL,8,Fhearing: "I think he was under stress
OL,9,Flooking after my mum but if it hadn't
OL,10,Fbeen for worries about inheritance tax
OL,11,Fhe would still be here today. He
OL,12,Fwouldn't have put us all through that
OL,13,Ffor any other reason.
OL,15,F"He thought he was doing it for the
OL,16,Fgood. I don't agree with that, but he
OL,17,Fthought he was doing it for the
OL,18,Fgreater good.
OL,26,@pD@JOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
